---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Membership"
  description="Learn how Studio Membership works at The Number Garden, including schedule, age format, and enrollment."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Membership</p>
      <h1>Studio Membership at The Number Garden.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Every family begins with a free family visit. If it feels like a fit,
        Studio Membership is the ongoing way to join the life of the studio:
        two visits each week, with rhythm and schedule finalized together after
        the visit.
      </p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="/family-visit/">
          Book a free family visit
        </a>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="/contact/">
          Ask a question
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="hero-card" aria-label="Membership summary">
      <p class="card-label">Studio Membership</p>
      <ul>
        <li>$400 per month</li>
        <li>Two visits each week</li>
        <li>Ages 3 to 5: caregiver + child</li>
        <li>Ages 6 and up: child-only</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <section class="panel panel-light">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">How It Works</p>
      <h2>Every family starts with a visit.</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="supporting-copy">
      The free family visit is where we get to know your child, talk about what
      you are hoping for, and decide whether The Number Garden feels like the
      right fit. If it does, Studio Membership is the next step.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="card-grid" aria-label="Membership details">
    <article class="topic-card">
      <h3>Two visits each week</h3>
      <p>
        Studio Membership is built around two weekly visits so children can
        develop continuity, confidence, and real momentum.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="topic-card">
      <h3>Age format</h3>
      <p>
        Ages 3 to 5 attend with a caregiver. Ages 6 and up move into a
        child-only format.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="topic-card">
      <h3>Current studio hours</h3>
      <p>
        Tuesday and Thursday from 3pm to 6pm, and Saturday from 9am to 11am.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="topic-card">
      <h3>Schedule is finalized together</h3>
      <p>
        Exact participation rhythm is worked out after the family visit, once
        we have a clearer sense of fit, age, and family needs.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="panel panel-accent contact-panel">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Enrollment</p>
      <h2>Enrollment follows the family visit.</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="contact-copy">
      If the visit makes it clear that The Number Garden is the right fit, I
      will follow up with the recommended schedule and next enrollment step,
      including the payment link for Studio Membership.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="button button-primary" href="/family-visit/">
        Book a free family visit
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
